title: A discombobulating ride with an aerobatics pilot
text: > Top News A discombobulating ride with an aerobatics pilot In this April 29, 2015, photo, Members of the flight crew push the plane carrying Associated Press sports writer John Marshall, seated front, and Red Bull plane racing pilot Kirby Chambliss onto the runway before Chambliss took Marshall on an aerobatic plane ride in Eloy, Ariz. Practicing three times a day, seven days a week, Chambliss turned himself into a five-time U.S. national aerobatics champion and was one of the founding pilots in the Red Bull Air Races when the series began in 2003. (AP Photo/Ross D. Franklin)
